<h3 class="date"><a href="/2008/jul/22/">&#x27a0;</a> July 22, 2008</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>This&#8217;ll make an AMAZING fort later</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/2693676388/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="This&#8217;ll make an AMAZING fort later" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3017/2693676388_cc8b9f45e7_m.jpg" height="240" width="180" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>In Somerville, we had a three-floor house with basement.  Now we have a one storey apartment. We used to have two offices and a spare room, now we have a combination office/spare room. Which will also hold my clothes, since we've got a smaller bedroom too.</p>

<p>In unrelated news, we'll be renting a storage locker shortly.</p>
        </p>

